overview.en: CLUB is committed to creating a global payment 2.0 era. Thousands of units such as shopping malls, plastic surgery hospitals, car shops, phone charges, fuel CARDS and so on have cooperated with the emperor group to jointly create the application scenarios of digital asset CLUB currency. The market has gradually won the mark and reputation.
overview.zh: CLUB致力于打造全球付2.0时代,在商城、整型医院、车行、充话费、冲油卡等数千家单位均与皇者集团合作，共同打造数字资产俱乐部CLUB币的应用场景，市场逐步获得记号口碑，让我们一起开创全新消费支付时代。
